Class WellAcquisitionData

java.lang.Object
  org.micromanager.metadata.WellAcquisitionData

public class WellAcquisitionData
extends java.lang.Object

Represents data structure associated with well acquisition. Well contains any number of imaging sites. Each imaging site is represented by a separate AcquistionData object
